data.description: This bright and open home has 3 bedrooms/2 baths, Big Great room with vaulted ceilings. Spacious kitchen with granite tops, big island and nice cabinetry.Bedrooms are roomy and so are the baths. Inside laundry and 2 car garage. Recent updates include: new A/C system installed. 50 amp electric rv hookup and  RV gate. 12.6 Malibu Catalina swim spa with 3 pumps, shade cover and on a concrete slab foundation. Close to Fool Hollow and Show Low city park.  This home has it all!
